Here's a preview of our all-new Patreon exclusive episode that finds the Losers recapping episodes three and four of Apple TV+'s Lisey's Story -- specifically, "Under the Yum-Yum Tree" and "Jim Dandy". Want more? Head on over to www.patreon.com/thebarrens and become a Patron for more exclusive bonus content.
